data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick ranch house nestled in the heart of Kettering. Meticulously updated, this home boasts a modernized kitchen adorned with sleek white cabinets, quartz countertops, tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The whole home's tile floor is equipped with radiant heating, ensuring warmth and comfort. The open layout seamlessly connects the family room, dining room, and living room, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Step outside to the screened-in patio that overlooks the fenced-in backyard, providing a perfect retreat for relaxation. Three generously sized bedrooms and an updated full bath are conveniently situated down the hall, offering both privacy and functionality. The primary bedroom features a tastefully updated ensuite bathroom. With a brand-new roof, this low-maintenance home is move-in ready, offering a perfect blend of modern amenities and timeless appeal.
